& [SLMSidecarTaskPromptContract] is the contract for task-specific sidecar prompt authority
  + [contract_uuid] is f7b740d9-8e36-4680-a195-dc522e3b5590
  + [slice_id] is SLM-35
  + [depends_on] is SLM_Sidecar_Evidence_Bundle_Contract, SLM_LM_Studio_Sidecar_Adapter_Contract, SLM_Provider_Internal_Faculty_Report_Contract
  + [status] is verified_wsl

  & [Purpose] is to prevent sidecar prompts from becoming hidden graph authority
    = must: define a task-specific instruction for every sidecar task kind
    = must: define allowed evidence for each task
    = must: define required output for each task
    = must: define forbidden authority for each task
    = must: require ProviderSuggestion output with rationale and provenance
    = must: preserve uncertainty when evidence does not justify resolution
    - never: allow sidecar output to create glyphs directly
    - never: allow sidecar output to rewrite EvidenceWorkspace records

  & [TaskContracts] are the v0 task set
    + [rank_senses] is contextual ranking of lexical sense candidates
    + [propose_spans] is bounded proposal of candidate spans from token and structure evidence
    + [object_to_parse] is objection to candidate meanings or relations with rationale
    + [answer_objection] is evidence-grounded answer to an objection
    + [run_faculty_validation] is seven-faculty dual-hemisphere validation report for a candidate

  & [AllowedEvidenceRule] is the prompt boundary
    = must: use only the SidecarEvidenceBundle, task target, question, and response contract
    = must: cite evidence refs in the returned ProviderSuggestion lineage or payload
    = must: prefer uncertainty output over unsupported certainty
    - never: use unstated world knowledge as if it were SLM evidence

  & [RequiredOutputRule] is the response boundary
    = must: return JSON matching LmStudioProviderSuggestionResponse
    = must: include provider_suggestions as an array
    = must: include rationale-bearing ProviderSuggestion payloads
    = must: use provider suggestion kinds rather than glyph identities
    - never: return prose outside JSON for machine sidecar calls

  & [MachineTemplate] is the source prompt contract artifact
    + [template] is slm_project/sidecar_prompts/sidecar_task_prompt_contracts_v0.json
    + [format] is slm_sidecar_task_prompt_contracts_v0

  & [RuntimeProjection] is the Rust source surface
    + [module] is slm_rust/src/sidecar.rs SidecarTaskPromptContract
    + [module] is slm_rust/src/sidecar.rs sidecar_task_prompt_contract
    + [module] is slm_rust/src/sidecar.rs task_instruction_text
    + [module] is slm_rust/src/sidecar.rs SidecarPromptEnvelope task_contract
    + [proof_route] is source gate and WSL cargo test

  ! [Slice35SourceComplete] is accepted
    @ [source_gate] passed with sidecar_prompt_contract_validation_ok tasks=5
    @ [wsl_cargo_test] passed 19 library tests and 3 slm_demo tests
    @ [regression_harness] passed slm_regression_harness_ok
    @ [template] is slm_project/sidecar_prompts/sidecar_task_prompt_contracts_v0.json
    @ [task_count] is 5
